The National Union of Electricity Employees (NUEE) has picked holes in the injection of over N3trn by Federal Government into privatised electricity companies.  So, what’s the logic to say government has no business in business, yet government has continued to pump and fund the business of individuals. We need to sit down and see what is working for us.
 
“If you put N2 trillion into the economy of Nigeria today, it will thrive better, yet such fund is being pumped into businesses owned by individuals.”